from chronic bronchitis.

168
00:22:48,125 --> 00:22:49,832
As an interesting side note,

169
00:22:49,917 --> 00:22:52,034
in spite of the
aforementioned anomalies,

170
00:22:52,125 --> 00:22:57,075
